  "title": "Silky Fresh Brazilian Bamboo Shoot Soup",
  "description": "A silky, crowd-pleasing Brazilian soup featuring tender bamboo shoots, coconut milk, and fermented fish sauce, all gluten-free and packed with fresh herbs.",
